wminc-code-macrolanguage: [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" language]] la anɛ [[wikipedia:ISO 639 macrolanguage|macrolanguage]],ka mɔr pian'ad banɛ dɔl la nwa:
wminc-code-collective: Koot kanɛ an "$1" la pʋ bɛɛ tis pian'ad yinne si'aa,amaa ka bɛɛ tis pian'ad gum sieba ka li yʋ'ʋr an ye [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" languages]]
wminc-code-retired: Pian'ad kaŋa koot la tiak ya ka pʋ lɛm bɛ tis Pin'ilʋg pian'ad la.
wminc-custom-editnotice-2: A-nyaŋi pa'an pian'ad banɛ ka fʋ nyaŋi nɔk tʋm la,bɛllimnɛ nɔkim $1 nwa tʋm. Tituunli, fʋ buudi pian'ad ya'a anɛ Kʋsaal ka fʋ na nyaŋi pian' Na'asaal sʋ'ʋŋa, nɔkim $2 tʋm
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-approved: Di siak di'e bama ka/bɛɛ li maal:
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-active: Bama vʋe bɛɛ tʋm ka li kʋ yuugɛ ba na di'e ba mɛŋ zin'ig:
wminc-custom-newarticletext-noprefix: Bɛllimnɛ baŋim: fʋ maan nɛ lakir ka [[$1|prefix]] kae.
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-3: Fʋ maan nɛ ([[$1|prefixed]])lakir paal ka li yʋ'ʋr an "{{FULLPAGENAME}}".
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-4: Mɛ Paasim prefixes nam tisi fʋ link nam nwa: [[Page title]] to [[Wx/xx/Page title]] and {{Page title}} to {{Wx/xx/Page title}}.
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-5: A-maal Nɛ'ɛŋa sʋ'ʋŋaa, fʋ tʋn'e zaŋ [[$1|Add prefix gate]] niŋ
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-title: Fʋ mɔɔd ye fʋ maal lakir nɛ yʋ'ʋgbɛlʋŋ
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-text:
Saŋa pamm yʋ'ʋr la pʋ mɔr [[$1|prefix]] bɛɛ di bɛnɛ suosi'a kanɛ mɔr gbɛlʋŋ ( banɛ mɔr vubiel bɛda bɛ prefix ni, nɛ trailing slash nɛ banɛ bɛ.).
Fʋ ya'a yinɛ zin'isi'a ke kpɛ' na,bɛllimnɛ lɛm ti maal link la ka yʋ'ʋn maal lakir ka li yʋ'ʋr dɔl tituaa. Fʋ ya'a mɔɔd nɛ ye kpa maal lakir la, bɛllimnɛ maalim lakir la li yʋ'ʋr dɔl bɛɛ tu'al tituaa.
Ka saŋa kanɛ ka nɛ'ɛŋa gu'udif ka fʋ kʋ nyaŋi maal lakir si'a kanɛ ka fʋ mi' sʋ'ʋŋa ye li mɔr yʋ'ʋr kanɛ an tituaa, bɛllimnɛ [[$2|kɛl ka Kpɛɛmnam baŋi li yɛla]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-title: Fʋ mɔɔd nɛ ye fʋ maal lakir kanɛ ka [[$1|ISO 639-1 bɛɛ -3 koot]] kanɛ tʋm kae
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-text:
Koot kaŋa pʋ tʋmma bɛɛ ka'a nɛ pian'ad kanɛ siak Wikipedia tʋʋm paala bʋnnɛ.
Fʋ ya'a yinɛ lakir si'a ni ke kpɛ' na,bɛllimnɛ lɛm ti maal link la ka nyaan maal lakir kanɛ yʋ'ʋri dɔl tituaa la.

ka li ya'a ti anɛ ye nɛ'ɛŋa gu'udif suor ka fʋ kʋ nyaŋi maal lakir si'a kanɛ ka fʋ tɛn'ɛs ye li mɔr koot ISO 639-3 bɛɛ -3 koot kanɛ tʋm bɛɛ an pian'ad kanɛ ka ba siak di'e, bɛllimnɛ [[$1|kɛl ka Kpɛɛmnam baŋi li yɛla ]]
wminc-custom-tb-space-colon: Baŋir tɔɔlim nam zug, yʋ'ʋr pʋ nar ye li pin'il nɛ paalʋ bɛɛ kɔlɔn.
gadget-addprefix: Add prefix: Zaŋim prefixes nam paas link namin saŋa kanɛ ka fʋ maan lakir.
wminc-gadget-addprefix-help: Di pʋ lɛn nar ye fʋ mɔr prefix la niŋid ya'asa fʋ ya'a ti dɛmisid lakir kaŋaa. Li mɛŋ na paas fʋ ya'a zaŋ lakir kaŋa pa'al sɔ' wʋsa.
gadget-interwiki: Interwiki: Paasimi li paŋ ka li paas ka pa'al sʋʋgin pian'ad suonɔya yi wikidata ni.
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-text: Nɔkim gbaʋŋ kaŋa n paas interwiki linknam dɔlisid wikidata laʋkin. Kʋdʋm nɔkim wikidata laʋk ID bɛɛ URL labil laʋk si'a bɛɛ sɔbʋg kanɛ dɛŋim maal bɛ pian'asi'a ni n bɛ gbinnin nwa ka din "{{int:wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-publish}}"
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-replace-text: Fʋ ya'a din "{{int:wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-publish}}", fʋ na lɛbig wiki kʋdʋr la tiak nɛ interwiki suonɔnya banɛ yi wikidata ni la n bɛ lakir kaŋa ni. Sɔb labaar kanɛ ka fʋ na zaŋ gaŋ wikidata laʋk la an linɛ dɔl nwa'.
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-replace-editinste: Ka lin na ya'a ka' sʋm, m bɛllimnɛ dɛmisim lakir la n sian'al suonɔɔr la sʋ'ʋŋa.
wminc-gadget-iw-error-invalid: Wikidata ID kanɛ ka kpɛn'ɛs la bɛɛ lakir kanɛ pa'a tɔ'ɔŋ la pʋ bɛɛ,  bɛɛ lakir la pʋ tɔ'ɔŋ nɛ wikidata. M bɛllimnɛ maligim mɔ ya'as.
wminc-gadget-iw-error-reload: M bɛllimnɛ maligim la'as lakir la ka mɔ ya'as.
tag-gadget-interwiki-description: Dɛmisa banɛ ka ba zaŋ interwiki masin bil nɔk interwiki suonɔnya paas.
gadget-settestwikipreference: Paasim "pian'ad maalʋg" ka maal (tʋʋma makir) ka li an fʋ tʋʋma makir bɔttɔn kanɛ wa'ae kpikpɛŋ fɔllin la, saŋa kanɛ ka fʋ gɔsid kpansib wiki nam.
wminc-gadget-twpref-setlang-tooltip: Maligim zi'el fʋn tʋm zin'isi'a pian'ad tis $1
wminc-gadget-twpref-setwiki: Maalim $1 ka li an fʋ tʋʋma makir
wminc-gadget-twpref-setwiki-tooltip: Maalim $1 ka li an fʋ tʋʋma makir, ala ka lakisa paala banɛ ka fʋ maal la na la'am paas tʋʋm kaŋa ni.
wminc-infopage-title-status-approved: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki makir ka ba siak di'e li bɛ Wikipedia Incubator ni
wminc-infopage-title-status-default: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki makir kanɛ bɛ Wikimedia Incubator la ni.
wminc-infopage-title-status-imported: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki makir kanɛ yi zin'isi'a na ka bɛ Wikipedia incubator la ni.
wminc-infopage-title-status-invalidcode: Wiki makir kaŋa mɔri pian'ad koot kanɛ pʋ vʋe ya, alazug li yiis ya [[$1|ISO 639]].
wminc-infopage-title-status-open: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki makir paalʋ kanɛ bɛ Wikimedia Incubator la ni.
wminc-infopage-title-status-rejected: Buudi pian'ad Kpɛɛmnam daa zan'as a-kpans wiki kaŋa nɛ ka yiisi li bas.
wminc-infopage-title-status-tocreate: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki paalʋ kanɛ bɛ Wikimedia Incubator la ni.
wminc-infopage-title-status-toimport: Nɛ'ɛŋa anɛ wiki makir kanɛ bɛ Wikipedia Incubator la ni ka bɔɔd ye yi kpɛn' kpɛ' na.
wminc-infopage-text-approved-prelangcom: Tʋʋm kanɛ ka ba daa bɔɔd la maali ya. Baŋim ye na daa siak di'e bɔɔdim kaŋa nɛ ka [[$3|language proposal policy]] zi'esim nyaan zaŋ tʋm, ka li pʋ sʋm ye li zaŋi lieb bʋnkanɛ an bɛog bɔɔdim nama (mɛ gɔsim [[$1|site creation log]]).
wminc-infopage-text-approved: [[$2|Language committee]] dim siaki di'e wiki makir kaŋa (mɛ gɔsim [[$1|site creation log]]).
wminc-infopage-text-default: Bɔdig bɛɛ gbɛlʋŋ paramita "$4". Gɔsim [[$5|kpɛla labaar bɛdegʋ]] kat wa'ae nɛ tɛmpulet kaŋa yɛla.
wminc-infopage-text-imported: Ba zaŋ wiki kaŋa yinɛ [[$6| zin'isi'a n kpɛn' kpɛla na]] wiki la daa yɔ la nya'aŋ. Fʋ ya'a bɔɔd ye fʋ (maligim pin'il) tʋʋm kaŋa, fʋ nɔk lakisa bama pin'ili li.
wminc-infopage-text-invalidcode: Wiki makir kaŋa mɔri pian'ad koot [[$7|ISO 639]] kanɛ pʋ vʋe ya, alazug li yiis ya. XML faal tʋn'e bɛ (bu'osim [[$8|the administrators]]) linɛ tʋn'e nyaŋi yiis tɔlis keŋ non-wikimedia wiki ni.
wminc-infopage-text-open: Wiki makir kaŋa yɔ'ɔg nɛ bɛɛ li pa'al nyain ye li mɔr suor si'el mɛkama ni. Kpɛmisidif ye fʋ sʋŋ paas pian'ad fʋ ya'a mi'i buudi pian'ad kaŋa. Mɛ gɔsim [[$9|the contribution manual]] tis pian' pa'al kat wa'ae nɛ linɛ nar ye fʋ maal.
wminc-infopage-text-rejected:
[[$2|Language
 Committee]] dim daa zan'as wiki makir kaŋa nɛ,ka yiisi li bas nyain. XML faal tʋn'e bɛ (bu'osim [[$8|Kpɛɛmnam la]]) linɛ na tʋn'e yiis tɔlis keŋ non-Wikimedia wiki ni.
wminc-infopage-text-tocreate: Wiki makir kaŋa nam pʋ pin'ilɛ. Fʋ ya'a buudi pian'ad kaŋa, fʋn dɔl nɔzi'ela la bɛ [[$9]]. Fʋ tʋn'e maal zug lakir bɛ "{{PAGENAME}}/zug_lakir" nɛ zug lakir ka li lɛbig bɛ pian'ad kaŋa ni (tituunli "WPA/fr/Accueil" li ya'a anɛ French wiki makir).
wminc-infopage-text-toimport: Wiki kaŋa yɔnɛ ka bɔɔd ye li yii kpɛn' kpɛla na. Fʋ ya'a na bɔɔd ye maligim pin'il tʋʋm kaŋa, m bɛllimnɛ gu'usum [[Special:ListUsers/import|importer]] ka ba ti zii lakisa wʋsa yi wiki mɛŋirin la yiiga.
wminc-infopage-text-awaiting-creation: Kpɛɛmnam la gu'usidi maalʋg ma'aa,  gɔsim "[[phabricator:$1|task $1]]".
wminc-infopage-language-setlang-na: Pian'ad kaŋa pʋ siaki an tʋʋm kanɛ ka fʋ tʋm nindaa la pian'ad nannanaa.
wminc-infopage-content-all-pages: Lakisa wʋsa banɛ bɛ kpansim wiki ni
wminc-infopage-req-unprefixed-templates: {{PLURAL: $1|$1 lakir|$1 lakisa}} bɛ dɔlisid unprefixed tɛmpulet namin.
wminc-infopage-req-error-wikisource: Tʋʋm kaŋa anɛ "Wikisource". Wikisource dɛmisa nar ye li maal bɛ [[$1|Multilingual Wikisource]] ni.
wminc-infopage-req-error-wikiversity: Tʋʋm kaŋa anɛ "wikiversity". Wikiversity dɛmisa nar ye li maal bɛ  [[$1|Beta Wikiversity]] la ni.
